# Project Name Contribution Guidelines

We welcome and appreciate contributions to Project Name. By contributing, you can help us improve the project and make it even better for the community. To ensure a smooth collaboration, please review and follow these guidelines when making contributions.

## How to Contribute

1. **Fork the Repository**: Click on the "Fork" button at the top right corner of the repository to create a copy under your GitHub account.

